item.title: Best of 2022: Film
item.description: Host Eric Rezsnyak, GPCD panelists Brendan Hay, Karissa Kloss, Kevin Dillon, and special guest Joey Moser ("Awards Daily") discuss their individual Top 3 picks for the best films of 2022. No debate, just a pop culture show-and-tell. Did your favorite flick make the list?
